import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import Exam01 from "./components/exam/Exam01.vue"
import Exam02 from "./components/exam/Exam02.vue"
import Switch from "./components/exam/03_Switch.vue"
import Radio from "./components/exam/04_Radio.vue"
import Container from "./components/exam/05_Container.vue"
import Tabbar from "./components/exam/06_Tabbar.vue"
import Fa from "./components/exam/08_Fa.vue"
import Home from "./components/message/Home.vue"
import MessageList from "./components/message/common/MessageList.vue"

Vue.use(Router)

export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/Exam01',component:Exam01},
    {path:'/Exam02',component:Exam02},
    {path:'/Switch',component:Switch},
    {path:'/Radio',component:Radio},
    {path:'/Container',component:Container},
    {path:'/Tabbar',component:Tabbar},
    {path:'/Fa',component:Fa},
    {path:'/Home',component:Home},
    {path:'/messagelist',component:MessageList},
  ]
})
